name: The YS Mat (By Kulae)-Black
description:
This is the ultimate eco yoga mat!  Outstanding support and comfort all in a 100% biodegradable yoga mat. 

At 72 inches long, 5mm thick and weighing less than 2.5 pounds, the YS Mat (By Kulae) is four inches longer than a standard yoga mat and has been designed with all styles of yoga in mind. This mat is revolutionary, and is the eco standard of yoga mats with a different color on each side giving the user the ability to use either side.

Made of Thermo Plastic Elastomer (É??TPEÉ?ù) | 100% Biodegradable | 100% Recyclable | Ultra-Hygienic | PVC- and Latex-Free

name: The YS Yoga Towel (By Kulae) -Orange
description:
The ultimate towel for grip, hygiene and comfort. The YS Towel (By Kulae) is antibacterial, antimicrobial, 100% recyclable and super-absorbent. This extra long and extra wide yoga towel is a great addition to your practice. This full-length yoga mat towel is 74 inches long and 25 inches wide making it a superior yoga towel for all styles of yoga and is a great accessory for the YS Mat.
For best results wash before first use.
Antibacterial | 100% Recyclable | Silicone-Free and Latex-Free | Ultra-Absorbent | Machine Washable

This long sleeved, cropped sweater features gently draping front panels that can be worn open and cascading, wrapped around the body, or secured at the neckline.

Toss this top over any sleeveless piece and embrace the warmth, softness and luxury of the Cuddle Me Wrap.

name: Vivacity Legging-Olivine-2
description:
The Vivacity Legging brings spunk to your legwear. The sleek and sexy legging features contrast stitching to highlight your best assets with just a hint of gold. The carefully placed Zari Mesh paneling shows a hint of skin, keeping you extra cool in a vigorous workout and extra stylish while out on the town.

Made of our signature Aurum+ fabric, these leggings offer an exceptionally flattering and comfortable fit.

description:
Add a kick of spice to your crops with the mystique of mesh. The beautifully constructed Vivacity Crop features contour panels with gold contrast stitching to elongate and tone the leg. Signature gold Zari Mesh paneling adds a hint of sparkle and nods to our gold standard products, giving just a peek of whatÉ??s underneath.

Keep cool during the most intense workouts and look sharp while out and about. Made of our signature Aurum+ Fabric, these crops offer an exceptionally flattering and comfortable fit.

description:

The Free & Easy Tank for yoga features a breezy design that stylishly hides what you want covered up and shows off everything else. Our flowy, soft Aurum 1064 drapes gently through the bodice and cinches at the hips to keep your figure in focus.

A thin racer back and lower armholes give a peek of whatÉ??s underneath (a bright strappy sports bra, perhaps?)É??without giving too much away. DonÉ??t worry about the fit of this tank. Expect effortless, Free & Easy style.

description: Our signature womenÉ??s short sleeve, the Bonjour Tee is ready to greet the day in style.  Breathable and airy Koura 24 fabric is as soft as your favorite cotton t-shirt, but has the antimicrobial and sweat wicking power of performance fabric. A soft-scooped neckline and feminine sleeves give this top a sophisticated and versatile look, while a subtle stitch down the center back elongates the torso. Pairing just as well with pencil skirts or yoga crops, the Bonjour tee is perfect for long flights, long meetings and long runs. Say hello to your newest wardrobe staple.
